    "name": "Mutants: Genesis",
    "steam_appid": 2138570,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138570/extras/63e89d2724456dbe15631ff5fd7000f6.poster.avif?t=1747734880\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138570/extras/63e89d2724456dbe15631ff5fd7000f6.webm?t=1747734880\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138570/extras/63e89d2724456dbe15631ff5fd7000f6.mp4?t=1747734880\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Mutants: Genesis: Unleash your mutants in the arena. The GCC where maps come to life</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in <i>Mutants: Genesis</i>, an explosive online card game where every card comes to life in a vibrant cyberpunk universe. Fast-paced combat, spectacular visuals and high-level strategy: <i>Mutants: Genesis</i> brings card games to life!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🎴 Animated cards for intense battles</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138570/extras/57e32bbfd7d735bf9ddab1cdc6757b36.poster.avif?t=1747734880\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138570/extras/57e32bbfd7d735bf9ddab1cdc6757b36.webm?t=1747734880\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138570/extras/57e32bbfd7d735bf9ddab1cdc6757b36.mp4?t=1747734880\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each ardc is animated, offering an immersive visual experience inspired by 90s comic books.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The battles are fast-paced and visually impressive, turning each duel into a real show.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🧬 Build your deck with unique Mutants</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138570/extras/cf7ea016d488b4186d5833ef570608af.poster.avif?t=1747734880\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138570/extras/cf7ea016d488b4186d5833ef570608af.webm?t=1747734880\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138570/extras/cf7ea016d488b4186d5833ef570608af.mp4?t=1747734880\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect over 200 cards spread across 6 distinct genes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create synergies between Mutants, Support Cards and Buildings to devise winning strategies.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🤝 Cooperate to defeat legendary Bosses</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138570/extras/bdde78f1e1247e369005565eb940ff9a.poster.avif?t=1747734880\" width=800 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138570/extras/bdde78f1e1247e369005565eb940ff9a.webm?t=1747734880\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138570/extras/bdde78f1e1247e369005565eb940ff9a.mp4?t=1747734880\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take part in cooperative battles for up to 3 players against powerful Bosses.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete weekly Time Rifts challenges for exclusive rewards.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🏆 <strong>Compete against other players and climb the rankings</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138570/extras/9a9f89e6fa8c96bf30a466410a3f5bc1.poster.avif?t=1747734880\" width=800 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138570/extras/9a9f89e6fa8c96bf30a466410a3f5bc1.webm?t=1747734880\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138570/extras/9a9f89e6fa8c96bf30a466410a3f5bc1.mp4?t=1747734880\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage in competitive PvP duels and progress from Bronze to Champion in dynamic seasons!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adapt your decks with regular balancing updates to stay on top.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🎁 Progress and unlock new cards</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138570/extras/d6b36a9e1e2d0886ae5d9c78b6cd7259.poster.avif?t=1747734880\" width=800 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138570/extras/d6b36a9e1e2d0886ae5d9c78b6cd7259.webm?t=1747734880\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138570/extras/d6b36a9e1e2d0886ae5d9c78b6cd7259.mp4?t=1747734880\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn cards and resources by playing PvP, PvE and completing daily, weekly and monthly challenges!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use these resources to craft new cards and improve your decks.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🌌 A rich and mysterious universe to explore</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as the latest prodigy at an orphanage training future Psycogs, tacticians capable of controlling Mutants. Discover the secrets that lurk in the shadows of this institution and forge your legend in tournaments around the world!Mutants: Genesis takes you through two story arcs that explore the game's universe!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
